ea7n qua, CLB Sunderland \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u sao tr\u1ebb MU Darron Gibson.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/photo1522629169079-1522629169079855832948.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018 do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u01b0ng thay v\u00ec t\u1eadp trung ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb, Gibson l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh khi b\u1ecb ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n l\u00e1i xe trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng say r\u01b0\u1ee3u h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng Ba v\u1eeba qua.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSunderland ban \u0111\u1ea7u treo gi\u00f2 Gibson 1 th\u00e1ng. Nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3, M\u00e8o \u0111en c\u1eaft \u0111\u1ee9t lu\u00f4n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y Gibson ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00f9i l\u1edbn n\u1eefa trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Man United. Khi c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, Gibson t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd k\u1ebf th\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Scholes. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n l\u1edbn anh t\u1ea1o ra l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Bayern \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2009/10 (2 b\u00ean h\u00f2a 4-4, Man United thua v\u00ec lu\u1eadt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch).<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTi\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng, Gibson kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 th\u00eam v\u00e0 d\u1ea7n m\u1ea5t \u0111i l\u00f2ng tin t\u1eeb Sir Alex. Anh chuy\u1ec3n sang Everton, thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gia nh\u1eadp Sunderland. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Gibson ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n d\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ee9c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. C\u00f2n Sunderland r\u1edbt kh\u1ecfi Premier League v\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 r\u01a1i t\u1eadn xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng 3 Anh. </div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"737","checkdouble":"183380"},{"date":"14:19 02/04","title":"Bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng nh\u00e0 Becks ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/2/biet-thu-vo-chong-nha-becks-tiep-tuc-gap-rac-roi.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolut