display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00edt t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia, Davide Iovinella v\u1eeba g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi b\u1ecf b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, chuy\u1ec3n sang \u0111\u00f3ng phim xxx.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/porn-actor-3.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi theo ngh\u1ec1 \u0111\u00f3ng phim ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn, Davide Iovinella kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu\u1ed9c Serie D, h\u1ea1ng T\u01b0 Italia, CLB ASD Calcio Pomigliano. V\u00ec thu nh\u1eadp \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1ecf Italia n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1ng n\u00ean ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 24 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ngh\u1ec1, chuy\u1ec3n sang \u0111\u00f3ng phim \"ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDavide Iovinella \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t may m\u1eafn l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n phim sex n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng Italia, \u00f4ng Rocco Siffredi. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Rocco Siffredi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, Davide Iovinella \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ebfn 3000 th\u00ed sinh kh\u00e1c, sau m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c thi di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t do ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n phim ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn 53 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y ch\u1ea5m thi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Davide Iovinella \u1edf Budapest (Hungary) tham gia b\u1ed9 phim ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn \u0111ang quay \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p m\u1edbi, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Italia cho hay: \u201cN\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng khi ng\u1ee7 v\u1edbi b\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00ed \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDavide Iovinella \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf h\u1eb3n \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t CLB m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n v\u00ec ngh\u1ec1 m\u1edbi gi\u00fap anh ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n.</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"734","checkdouble":"183386"},{"date":"15:10 02/04","title":"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u00ea C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 HAGL","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/4/6/hlv-le-thuy-hai-tiep-tuc-che-cong-phuong-va-hagl.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f