r:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, G\u0110KT Chung Hae Soung t\u1ecf ra khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i V-League 2018 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"GDKT Chung Hae Soung noi gi sau thang loi dau tay cua HAGL hinh anh\" title=\"G\u0110KT Chung Hae Soung n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ea7u tay c\u1ee7a HAGL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/gdkt-chung-hae-seong-khiem-ton-sau-tran-thang-cua-hagl1522652819.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>G\u0110KT Chung Hae Soung trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1/4 v\u1eeba qua, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-hagl-vs-nam-dinh-19h00-ngay-14-vleague-2018-372-183307.html\" target=\"_blank\">chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2</span> kh\u00e1 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pleiku tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. \u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n v\u00e0 H\u1ed3ng Duy l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng cho HAGL tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 2 b\u00e0n thua t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ea7u tay \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League 2018</span>, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 HAGL t\u1ef1 tin b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, G\u0110KT Chung Hae Soung t\u1ecf ra khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: \"M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL v\u1eeba thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup v\u1edbi Jordan, th\u1ebf n\u00ean ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 ng\u00e0y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb. Trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, th\u1ebf n\u00ean t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0103n m\u1eebng 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i. HAGL s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n cho nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o th\u1ee9 N\u0103m t\u1edbi, HAGL s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o th\u1eed th\u00e1ch l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi khi c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. C\u0169ng b\u1edfi chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 H\u1ed3ng Duy thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Ngay c\u1ea3 th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169ng s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00fat ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i 5/4 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/5-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-hagl-32-nam-dinh-168-183338.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/1/5-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-hagl-32-nam-dinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/5-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-hagl-32-nam-dinh-168-183338.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-2 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u tay t\u1ea1i V-League 2018. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span sty