 #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 3/4.<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/david-de-gea-43863.html\">De Gea</span> gia h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</strong> Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 2 b\u00ean chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t. Theo \u0111\u00f3, David De Gea s\u1ebd g\u1eafn b\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-13-tottenham-ca-thang-tu-va-tro-dua-mang-ten-conte-172-183342.html\">Man United</span> trong 5 n\u0103m t\u1edbi, nh\u1eadn <strong>m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 350 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diem tin bong da 24h sang 34 De Gea gia han 5 nam voi Quy do hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h s\u00e1ng 34 De Gea gia h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/14/Diem-tin-bong-da-24h-sang-34-De-Gea-gia-han-5-nam-voi-Quy-do-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 3/4: De Gea s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Man-City-1471.html\">Man xanh</span> \u201ckh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m ch\u1ea5p\u201d Man \u0111\u1ecf.</strong> Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, Pep Guardiola v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u0103ng quang, n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn derby 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Man United cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u01b0u ti\u00ean m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn Champions League v\u1edbi 2 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Liverpool h\u01a1n, v\u00ec v\u1eady \u00f4ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<strong>\u00a0</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea mu\u1ed1n Conte \u0111i s\u1edbm.</strong> Gianluca Vialli, c\u1ef1u ch\u00e2n s\u00fat The Blues m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-13-tottenham-ca-thang-tu-va-tro-dua-mang-ten-conte-172-183342.html\">Antonio Conte n\u00ean t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c </span>c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Premier League, Cup C1, Cup Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 4, sau khi b\u1ecb Spurs b\u1ecf c\u00e1ch 8 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n<strong>\u00a0</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Bayern l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Man-City-1471.html\">Real Madrid</span>. </strong>HLV Jupp Heynckes kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Robert Lewandowski. \u00cdt ng\u00e0y qua, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Bernabeu v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro, tuy nhi\u00ean H\u00f9m x\u00e1m kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng CLB c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u01b0\u1edbp \u0111i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 3/4: Robert Lewandowski l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng\" title=\"tien dao Robert Lewandowski\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/22/Real-bo-Kane-mua-Lewandowski-trong-mua-he-toi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Robert Lewandowski l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nUmtiti th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a v\u1ed9i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.</strong> M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man United theo \u0111u\u1ed5i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/samuel-umtiti-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-180-183369.html\">Samuel Umtiti \u0111ang gi\u1edf th\u00f3i \u201cc\u00f2 c\u01b0a\u201d v\u1edbi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n </span>Barcelona, khi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n gia h\u1ea1n l\u00fac n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Umtiti mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 9 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a, v\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn Barca c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u2013 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div>\r\n<br></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"730","checkdouble":"183406"},{"date":"06:52 03/04","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Cup C1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Liverpool l\u1ea5y Salah ra d\u1ecda Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/truoc-tu-ket-cup-c1-nguoi-liverpool-lay-salah-ra-doa-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}