; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Trong cu\u1ed9c n\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh gi\u1eefa Liverpool vs Man City, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Virgil Van Dijk ca ng\u1ee3i Salah khi cho r\u1eb1ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Van Dijk ca ng\u1ee3i Salah \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 l\u1eddi khen \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1eebng ghi b\u00e0n, v\u00e0 \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn nay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ngay c\u1ea3 Man City ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa, c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp, hay \u00edt nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a anh ngh\u0129. V\u1edbi 29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng, 37 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/mohamed-salah-148052.html\">Mohamed Salah</span> \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi 21 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c nhau c\u1ee7a CR7 v\u00e0 Robin Van Persie tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 theo Van Dijk, anh bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Salah s\u1ebd m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Man City, v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au-c184-p1.html\">Champions League</span>: &ldquo;T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Salah l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n c\u1ea7n ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n. Khi \u1edf phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t, <strong>c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o</strong>.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Van Dijk ca ngoi Salah truoc them chien Man City hinh anh\" title=\"Van Dijk ca ng\u1ee3i Salah tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m chi\u1ebfn Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/salah.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Van Dijk ca ng\u1ee3i Salah tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u1ef1c ra, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Salah, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Man-City-1471.html\">Man City</span> suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3&rdquo; &ndash; H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u00fap m\u1edf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ca ng\u1ee3i, nh\u01b0ng Mo Salah v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n v\u00e0 ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9. Anh kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh xa \u00e1nh h\u00e0o quang t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Van Dijk ca ng\u1ee3i Salah v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Liverpool h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i: &ldquo;V\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n, trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Mohamed l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai trong CLB. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<strong> Kh\u00f4ng ai l\u00e0 si\u00eau sao, kh\u00f4ng ai c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh hay h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c</strong>, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 nhau v\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/mane-tin-tuong-salah-se-vui-dap-man-city-184-183401.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/31/mane-tin-tuong-salah-se-vui-dap-man-city.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/mane-tin-tuong-salah-se-vui-dap-man-city-184-183401.html\">Mane tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Salah s\u1ebd v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Man City</span><br>\r\nSadio Mane tin r\u1eb1ng Salah c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Man City t\u1ea1i Champions League khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam mai.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/pep-guardiola-thua-nhan-khong-co-cach-ngan-can-bo-ba-cua-liverpool-184-183375.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/15/pep-guardiola-thua-nhan-khong-co-cach-ngan-can-bo-ba-cua-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/pep-guardiola-thua-nhan-khong-co-cach-ngan-can-bo-ba-cua-liverpool-184-183375.html\">Pep Guardiola th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n b\u1ed9 ba c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span><br>\r\nHLV Pep Guardiola kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n v\u00f4 hi\u1ec7u h\u00f3a b\u1ed9 ba Salah, Mane v\u00e0 Firmino c\u1ee7a Liverpool.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"729","checkdouble":"183410"},{"date":"08:09 03/04","title":"Chiellini ca ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo, th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/chiellini-ca-ngoi-ronaldo-than-trong-truoc-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-fa