ound-position:-80px -224px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-tl{border-top-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au-c184-p1.html\">t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Cup C1</span> gi\u1eefa Juventus vs Real Madrid, trung v\u1ec7 Giorgio Chiellini \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ca ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ecf Cris Ronaldo l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng, nh\u01b0ng trung v\u1ec7 Italia v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1edbi CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn Juventus vs Real Madrid, trung v\u1ec7 Chiellini cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/cristiano-ronaldo-44953.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo</span> l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1eady, Sergio Ramos l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Real Madrid, s\u1ebd th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ecd. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Ronaldo, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Real kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1eady.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n anh ta m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n sai l\u1ea7m. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng cho Real Madrid.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Juventus vs Real Madrid l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Chiellini \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i m\u00f3n n\u1ee3\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Juventus vs Real Madrid, Chiellini ca ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/ch.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Juventus vs Real Madrid l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Chiellini \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i m\u00f3n n\u1ee3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u00e1m \u1ea3nh b\u1edfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Los Blancos, trung v\u1ec7 Italia ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n tr\u1ea3 th\u00f9 hay \u0111\u1ea1i lo\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, b\u1edfi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c v\u1edbi to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 CLB h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Barca, Real hay Bayern Munich.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1edb k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y vui v\u1ebb t\u1ea1i Cadiff (chung k\u1ebft Cup C1 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i), nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c. <strong>Juventus \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</strong>&rdquo; &ndash; <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/giorgio-chiellini-44610.html\">Giorgio Chiellin</span>i k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, HLV c\u1ee7a Juve &ndash; Max Allegri c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn: &ldquo;B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i cho Ronaldo. Anh \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i \u1edf trung t\u00e2m theo m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c th\u01b0\u1eddng, b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi b\u1ea1n b\u01b0\u1edbc sang \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 30.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Paulo Dybala c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi AC Milan v\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/juventus-vs-real-madrid-tai-tu-ket-c1-oan-gia-ngo-hep-184-182202.html\">Juventus vs Real Madrid</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Miralem Pjanic v\u00e0 Mehdi Benatia v\u00ec \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa Juventus vs Real Madrid</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/14088659/003100\">Juve vs Real<br>\r\n</span><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/zidane-truoc-tran-juventus-vs-real-madrid-184-183395.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/19/zidane-truoc-tran-juventus-vs-real-madrid.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/zidane-truoc-tran-juventus-vs-real-madrid-184-183395.html\">Zidane c\u1ea3nh t\u1ec9nh h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Juventus</span><br>\r\nHLV Zinedine Zidane kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a g\u00ec khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Juventus.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"728","checkdouble":"183417"},{"date":"08:09 03/04","title":"Sao Bayern: \u201cSevilla c\u0169ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 B