0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, trong tr\u1eadn Sevilla vs Bayern Munich. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Bayern-Munich-1567.html\">H\u00f9m x\u00e1m</span> v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/javi-martinez-43877.html\">Javi Martinez</span> cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;C\u00f3 l\u1ebd m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Sevilla l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n sai l\u1ea7m, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd c\u0169ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 Barca hay Real Madrid. N\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, CLB T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Manchester-United-1.html\">Man United</span> ngay t\u1ea1i Old Trafford, qua \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Cup C1. Martinez ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00ed d\u1ee5 \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Sevilla x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U \u1edf c\u1ea3 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111i v\u00e0 v\u1ec1.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Truoc them Sevilla vs Bayern Munich, Javi Martinez noi gi hinh anh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m Sevilla vs Bayern Munich, Javi Martinez n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/martinez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martinez th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Sevilla vs Bayern Munich</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecd. Sevilla r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u quan tr\u1ecdng&rdquo; &ndash; C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Athletic Bilbao ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;SV\u0110 Sanchez Pizjuan r\u1ea5t \u1ed3n \u00e0o, c\u00e1c C\u0110V g\u00e0o th\u00e9t trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn. Khi c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Bilbao v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla, \u0111\u00f3 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed n\u00e1o nhi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o h\u00f4m nay v\u1edbi Bayern, b\u1edfi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Sevilla r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi h\u1ecd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au-c184-p1.html\">Champions League</span>.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Jupp Heynckes c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem nh\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng l\u1edbn cho Sevilla. H\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00f3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng, phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i sau l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m r\u1eb1ng Sevilla l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c CLB c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh&rdquo; &ndash; HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/sevilla-vs-bayern-munich-01h45-ngay-0404-sanchez-pizjuan-nuot-tron-hum-xam-184-183405.html\">Sevilla vs Bayern Munich</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/sevilla-vs-bayern-munich-01h45-ngay-0404-sanchez-pizjuan-nuot-tron-hum-xam-184-183405.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/Preview-Sevilla-vs-Bayern-Munich.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/sevilla-vs-bayern-munich-01h45-ngay-0404-sanchez-pizjuan-nuot-tron-hum-xam-184-183405.html\">Sevilla vs Bayern Munich (01h45 ng\u00e0y 04/04): Sanchez Pizjuan s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nu\u1ed1t tr\u1ecdn &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Sevilla vs Bayern Munich \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft C1, s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Sanchez Pizjuan s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a TBN hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc &ldquo;H\u00f9m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"727","checkdouble":"183418"},{"date":"08:18 03/04","title":"Juventus vs Real Madrid (01h45 ng\u00e0y 4/4): Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3 th\u00f9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/3/juventus-vs-real-madrid-01h45-ngay-44-chua-the-tra-thu.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:no