 b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Cadiff, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Max Allegri s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f2i n\u1ee3 trong tr\u1eadn Juventus vs Real Madrid v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e1ng 6/2017, x\u1ee9 Wales ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa 2 CLB m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/juventus-vs-real-madrid-01h45-ngay-44-chua-the-tra-thu-184-183419.html\">Juventus vs Real Madrid</span>. Hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 1-1, nh\u01b0ng b\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft 2017 gi\u1eefa Juventus vs Real Madrid l\u00e0 k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m bu\u1ed3n v\u1edbi CLB Italia\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng\u0111\u00e124h Juventus vs Real Madrid t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Cup C1 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/Nhan-dinh-bongda24h-Juventus-vs-Real-Madrid-tu-ket-Cup-C1-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft 2017 gi\u1eefa Juventus vs Real Madrid l\u00e0 k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m bu\u1ed3n v\u1edbi CLB Italia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLos Blancos \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ph\u00e1 b\u1ecf l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au-c184-p1.html\">Champions League</span>. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Juve, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a L\u00e3o b\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 suy gi\u1ea3m th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, sau khi 2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00f4i qua 45 ph\u00fat, v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 (t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, pressing).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">10 th\u00e1ng tr\u00f4i qua, 2 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ea1i g\u1eb7p nhau, l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/juventus-42.html\">Juve</span> \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c x\u01b0a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8. Leo Bonucci \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i, v\u00e0 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 Szczesny, De Sciglio, Bentancur, Bernardesch, Howedes v\u00e0 Matuidi. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/real-madrid-29.html\">Real Madrid</span> kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, khi ch\u1ec9 \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng c\u00f2n y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Alvaro Morata v\u00e0 James Rodriguez. Tuy v\u1eady, <strong>s\u1ebd l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m n\u1ebfu coi th\u01b0\u1eddng Los Blancos</strong>, b\u1edfi HLV Zidane v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9 khung, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus vs Real Madrid t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League\" title=\"Juventus vs Real Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/16/juventus-vs-real-madrid-tai-tu-ket-c1-oan-gia-ngo-hep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus vs Real Madrid t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Juve v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Serie A, d\u00f9 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Real Madrid l\u1ea1i ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 n\u1eeda m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1ee9t \u0111i, b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn tham d\u1ef1, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed7i Champions League \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/cristiano-ronaldo-44953.html\">Cris Ronaldo</span> v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. CR7 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea1n, c\u00f2n Real Madrid m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 cho nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0u PSG th\u1ea5y kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. M\u1ed9t Real \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn chung, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a 2 b\u00ean c\u0169ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juve t\u1ecf ra e ng\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/truoc-dai-chien-buffon-len-tieng-khen-ngoi-ronaldo-184-183123.html\">Buffon s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh b\u1ecb Ronaldo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi</span>; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, ngay khi h\u1ecd b\u1ed1c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e1 th\u0103m Juventus.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus vs Real Madrid t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Cup C1\" title=\"Juve \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Milan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/juve.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juve c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft C1 b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>D\u0129 d\u1eadt \u0111\u00e3i lao<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c nhau, s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Juventus vs Real Madrid tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, L\u00e3o b\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/tong-hop-juventus-31-ac-milan-vong-30-serie-a-201718-327-183274.html\">gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc AC Milan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-1</span>, nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i c\u00e0y \u1ea3i su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, 2 ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/mario-mandzukic-44453.html\">Mario Mandzukic</span> v\u00e0 Alex Sandro ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Medhi Benatia v\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/miralem-pjanic-44113.html\">Miralem Pjanic</span> ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t v\u00ec \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2. \u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn t\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0, v\u00e0 Allegri \u0111ang r\u1ea5t b\u1ed1i r\u1ed1i trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, HLV Zidane c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 binh h\u00f9ng t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1ea1nh trong tay, h\u01a1n n\u1eefa c\u00f2n \u1edf tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i sung s\u1ee9c nh\u1ea5t. Ronaldo, Marcelo v\u00e0 Ramos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ngh\u1ec9 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (th\u1eafng Las Palmas 3-0), trong khi b\u1ed9 ba ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Kroos &ndash; Modric &ndash; Casemiro c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ra ngh\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, Real Madrid \u0111ang d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc trong kh\u00e2u chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb, khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn trong tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu khi\u1ebfn Juve thua th\u1ea3m \u1edf chung k\u1ebft n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa Real s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t, khi d\u00f9ng s\u1ee9c nh\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1ee9c m\u1ecfi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Zidane s\u1edf h\u1eefu phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Juventus vs Real Madrid\" title=\"Real thang Las Palmas 3-0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/thay-gi-sau-tran-dau-las-palmas-vs-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid c\u0169ng \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, Juve v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3, l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, khi <strong>Juve 4 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1 bay \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out</strong>, v\u1edbi th\u1ec3 th\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i &ndash; l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 th\u00f4i l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n b\u01b0\u1edbc, hay xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Los Blancos. V\u00e0 trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i gi\u1eefa <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/juventus-vs-real-madrid-tai-tu-ket-c1-oan-gia-ngo-hep-184-182202.html\">Juventus vs Real Madrid</span> t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n Max Allegri ph\u1ea3i \u00f4m h\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin b\u00ean l\u1ec1<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Real Madrid th\u1eafng 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Real Madrid ghi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn, trong 17/21 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Real Madrid th\u1eafng 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Real Madrid th\u1eafng 11/13 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Ronaldo ghi 23 b\u00e0n trong 13 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, v\u00e0 7 b\u00e0n trong 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p Juve.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Juventus b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Juventus b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 7 cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Real Madrid tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 (6 th\u1eafng, 1 h\u00f2a).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Juventus b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 25 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 21 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Juventus ghi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn, trong 3 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Juventus gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 11/13 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, t\u00ednh tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Trong 4 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i &ndash; l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1), Juve \u0111\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i Real.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Trong 21 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u, Real Madrid th\u1eafng 9, Juventus th\u1eafng 8 v\u00e0 h\u00f2a 2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Miralem Pjanic v\u00e0 Medhi Benatia do \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2. Bernardeschi v\u00e0 Alex Sandro c\u0169ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 quay l\u1ea1i luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp, v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Mario Mandzukic ch\u01b0a b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, HLV Zidane c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, Cris Ronaldo, Ramos v\u00e0 Marcelo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Los Blancos l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Nacho.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Giorgio Chiellini, Alex Sandro v\u00e0 Rodrigo Bentancur c\u1ee7a Juventus, c\u00f9ng Sergio Ramos c\u1ee7a Real Madrid s\u1ebd l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\n</strong> <br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Juventus vs Real Madrid\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Juventus vs Real Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/Juventus-vs-Real-Madrid-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-3-1-2).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Juventus vs Real Madrid</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 Juventus vs Real Madrid:</strong> 1-2<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/chiellini-ca-ngoi-ronaldo-than-trong-truoc-real-madrid-184-183417.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/chiellini-ca-ngoi-ronaldo-than-trong-truoc-real-madrid.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/chiellini-ca-ngoi-ronaldo-than-trong-truoc-real-madrid-184-183417.html\">Chiellini ca ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo, th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Cup C1 gi\u1eefa Juventus vs Real Madrid, trung v\u1ec7 Giorgio Chiellini \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ca ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/zidane-truoc-tran-juventus-vs-real-madrid-184-183395.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/19/zidane-truoc-tran-juventus-vs-real-madrid.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/zidane-truoc-tran-juventus-vs-real-madrid-184-183395.html\">Zidane c\u1ea3nh t\u1ec9nh h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Juventus</span><br>\r\nHLV Zinedine Zidane kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a g\u00ec khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Juventus.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"726","checkdouble":"183419"},{"date":"09:14 02/04","title":"Mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u201cMessi Ai C\u1eadp\u201d, Real ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/18/real-madrid-mua-mohamed-salah-phai-dap-ung-2-dieu-kien.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size: