1ea3i t\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 Salah, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi 29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mua Mohamed Salah phai dap ung 2 dieu kien hinh anh\" title=\"Real Madrid mua Mohamed Salah ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng 2 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/real-madrid-mua-mohamed-salah-phai-dap-ung-2-dieu-kien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid mua Mohamed Salah c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nReal d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh s\u1ebd bi\u1ebfn Salah tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi. H\u1ecd xem c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mo-salah-messi-ai-cap-hay-mot-su-so-sanh-lo-bich-172-183227.html\" target=\"_blank\">&ldquo;Messi Ai C\u1eadp&rdquo;</span> nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho Gareth Bale \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Salah, anh \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gia nh\u1eadp Real. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Roma kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e2m v\u00e0o ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb xoay v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 Gareth Bale hay m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean kh\u00e1c. Anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, Salah c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 l\u1edbn. Ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp sau Cristiano Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn 32 tri\u1ec7u Euro/ n\u0103m v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y (th\u1ee9 3 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ch\u1ec9 sau Lionel Messi v\u00e0 Neymar). \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u Real Madrid mua Mohamed Salah \u0111\u1eafn \u0111o nh\u1ea5t b\u1edfi lo s\u1ee3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Mohamed Salah tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sau-coutinho-barca-lai-muon-co-them-ca-salah-180-183294.html\">Sau Coutinho, Barca l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u1ea3 Salah</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/salah-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-sau-ban-thang-vao-luoi-palace-172-183264.html\">Ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t Palace, Salah h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 40 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mohamed-salah-lap-ky-luc-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-ban-thang-vao-luoi-crystal-palace-172-183249.html\">Mohamed Salah l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c: \u0110i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Crystal Palace</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\