display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n s\u1eafp chuy\u1ec3n sang M.U, Samuel Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Samuel Umtiti s\u1ebd r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Barcelona trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. \u0110i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 60 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i gia mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eb1m mang anh v\u1ec1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nUmtiti \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mourinho-chi-102-trieu-bang-nang-cap-hang-thu-mu-172-183316.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>M.U v\u00e0 HLV Jose Mourinho</strong></span> trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Barca v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi anh \u0111\u1ec3 &ldquo;c\u01a1i n\u1edbi&rdquo; l\u1ea1i s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Samuel Umtiti phat bieu ve tuong lai va Barca hinh anh\" title=\"Samuel Umtiti ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0 Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/samuel-umtiti-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\">Samuel Umtiti ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u00ean Canal +<br>\r\n            </span></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tu-choi-cam-ket-voi-barca-umtiti-se-sang-man-united-172-182867.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Samuel Umtiti</strong></span> ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai cho bi\u1ebft c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Man United v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f3 s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 CLB nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i xin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c&rdquo;, Umtiti n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Canal +. &ldquo;Tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, s\u1ef1 v\u1eadt chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t nhanh nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Barcelona. &rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u00ec c\u1ea3. C\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Barca, nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-chi-102-trieu-bang-nang-cap-hang-thu-mu-172-183316.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/31/mourinho-chi-102-trieu-bang-nang-cap-hang-thu-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-chi-102-trieu-bang-nang-cap-hang-thu-mu-172-183316.html\">Mourinho chi 102 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 MU</span><br>\r\n<span>Man United \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Alex Sandro v\u00e0 Samuel Umtiti \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua l\u1ea1i 60 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Umtiti n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. N\u00f3 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i qu\u00e1 b\u1eadn t\u00e2m. T\u00f4i ch\u00fa \u00fd h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a Umtiti. Anh c\u00f3 22 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Barca t\u1ea1i La Liga v\u00e0 34 tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Samuel Umtiti tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n</strong><strong><br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-chi-102-trieu-bang-nang-cap-hang-thu-mu-172-183316.html\">Mourinho chi 102 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-mua-lucas-hernandez-cua-atletico-madrid-180-183303.html\">Barca nh\u1eafm &ldquo;h\u00e0ng hot&rdquo; ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba M.U cu\u1ed7m Umtiti</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shaw-duoc-dem-lam-vat-te-than-de-mourinho-mua-sao-barca-172-183111.html\">Shaw \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em l\u00e0m v\u1eadt t\u1ebf th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 Mourinho mua sao Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tu-choi-cam-ket-voi-barca-umtiti-se-sang-man-united-172-182867.html\">T\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i cam k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Barca, Umtiti s\u1ebd sang Man United?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-bat-ngo-muon-hut-mau-barca-180-182255.html\">Real Madrid b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n h\u00fat m\u00e1u Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nGia Vi (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"724","checkdouble":"183369"},{"date":"14:51 02/04","title":"HLV Diego Simeone: \"Messi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/2/messi.PNG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left