 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Diego Simeone phat bieu ve Lionel Messi hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Diego Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/HLV-Diego-Simeone-phat-bieu-ve-Lionel-Messi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nPh\u00fat 88, Suarez r\u00fat ng\u1eafn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 1-2, 1 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3 Messi l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2. Ch\u00ednh s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a M10 gi\u00fap Barca r\u1eddi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Sevilla v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Sevilla l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9 26 c\u1ee7a Messi \u1edf La Liga, anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-messi-giai-cuu-barca-du-chua-khoi-chan-thuong-180-183282.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Messi ch\u01b0a b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng </strong></span>nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn v\u00e0o s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla, d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u00f3 30 ph\u00fat nh\u01b0ng anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. M10 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Barca, 44 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 anh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Diego Simeone khen ng\u1ee3i Lionel Messi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Diego Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc: \u201cNh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Sevilla \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Kh\u00f4ng Messi, Barca thua 0-2, c\u00f3 Messi Barca g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap Barca chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Diego Simeone phat bieu ve Lionel Messi\" title=\"HLV Diego Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/messi.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Diego Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cMessi x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Barca. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/lionel-messi-44368.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Messi</strong></span> trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y\u201d, HLV Simeone ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAtletico v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Deportivo 1-0 \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00fat ng\u1eafn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi Barca tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng La Liga xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m, n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: \u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung \u0110TQG, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Atletico c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Messi \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/12994-42556/033100\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Messi \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"723","checkdouble":"183382"},{"date":"14:48 02/04","title":"Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Real thanh l\u00fd 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong H\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias