arget=\"_blank\">Champions League</span>, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u thay m\u00e1u l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong h\u00e8 2018. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, Cristiano Ronaldo c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ra 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u00e0 BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea7n thanh l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng h\u01a1n trong h\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo muon Real thanh ly 7 cau thu trong He 2018  hinh anh\" title=\"Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Real thanh l\u00fd 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong H\u00e8 2018  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/Ronaldo-muon-Real-thanh-ly-7-cau-thu-trong-He-2018--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Real thanh l\u00fd 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, bao g\u1ed3m Isco</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin Diario Gol, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Real thanh l\u00fd 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Isco. Theo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng CR7 c\u1ea3 trong l\u1eabn ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. C\u1ea3 hai kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi nhau. V\u00ec v\u1eady, CR7 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n th\u1ea5y Isco \u1edf s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, QBV th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 2017 c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n Los Blancos s\u1edbm t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Keylor Navas, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 32 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 12 t\u1edbi. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 trong c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Real-Madrid-29.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real</span> trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a th\u00e1nh Iker tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o Keylor Navas t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 y\u00ean t\u00e2m v\u1edbi Ronaldo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e3 th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Real Madrid mang v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 De Gea v\u00e0 Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Navas. V\u00e0 anh \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p m\u1edbi \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef khung th\u00e0nh trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, trong danh s\u00e1ch thanh l\u00fd m\u00e0 Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Real th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Mateo Kovacic, Marcos Llorente, Borja Mayoral, Jesus Vallejo v\u00e0 Achraf Hakimi. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb m\u00e0 CR7 cho r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia trong m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;&#10;font-family:Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/750-42556/033100\">Cristiano Ronaldo</span></strong><br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%;font-family:Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<br></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"722","checkdouble":"183383"},{"date":"20:41 02/04","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t HLV \u1edf Premier League ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/2/them-mot-hlv-o-premier-league-chinh-thuc-mat-viec.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style