ilter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u00ean gia ph\u00e2n t\u00edch Garth Crooks cho r\u1eb1ng HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Lingard nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho bi chi trich vi Lingard hinh anh\" title=\"Mourinho b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec Lingard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/mourinho-bi-chi-trich-vi-cach-dung-lingard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lingard \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lingard \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Lingard cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u1ea1i Amsterdam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i b\u1edfi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Man United v\u00e0 Swansea cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, chuy\u00ean gia Garth Crooks \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mourinho v\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Lingard qu\u00e1 d\u00e8 d\u1eb7t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u00ec bu\u1ed9c Mourinho ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ea v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cLingard ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ph\u1ea3i n\u1eb1m trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh tham d\u1ef1 World Cup. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cHLV Mourinho c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Lingard m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u00e8 d\u1eb7t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5 m\u1ecdi ch\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Mourinho. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, b\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 c\u00e1c show di\u1ec5n t\u1ea1i Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cLingard c\u00f3 in d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc Swansea. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u1ecdi c\u1ef1 ly. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 Gareth Southgate c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng c\u1ea3 Lingard v\u00e0 Alli trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hay kh\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng h\u01a1i gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 Steven Gerrard v\u00e0 Frank Lampard d\u1eabm ch\u00e2n nhau tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y\u201d.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juan-mata-danh-loi-khen-dac-biet-cho-lukaku-172-183402.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/2/juan-mata-danh-loi-khen-dac-biet-cho-lukaku.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juan-mata-danh-loi-khen-dac-biet-cho-lukaku-172-183402.html\">Juan Mata d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t cho Lukaku</span><br>\r\n<span>Juan Mata v\u1eeba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Romelu Lukaku th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLingard \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 24 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Anh \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 4 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0ng Lingard v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Sanchez, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 \u01b0u \u00e1i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 10 thay v\u00ec Lingard. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua, qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea9y Lingard l\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh Sanchez m\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n v\u00e0 l\u00e2m v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"719","checkdouble":"183404"},{"date":"07:09 03/04","title":"De Bruyne: \u201cT\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/11/de-bruyne-toi-xung-dang-gianh-giai-cau-thu-hay-nhat-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration